title: Jual beli tanah dan pencatatan peralihan hak

description.value: Transfer of land titles according to Indonesian laws and regulations.

notes.value:
Originally presented as the author's thesis (master's--Universitas Indonesia) under title: Larangan badan usaha pengembang perumahan dan permukiman menjual tanah tanpa bangunan berkaitan dengan pencatatan peralihan hak dalam sertipikat tanda bukti hak atas tanah, studi analisis di PT X.

"Peraturan perundang-undangan": p. [72]-[74].

Includes bibliographical references (p. [68]-[72]).
